1965年，法联航的六架使用[[涡轮喷气发动机|涡喷引擎]]的DC-8-30逐渐改装为使用[[渦輪扇發動機|涡扇引擎]]的DC-8-50。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1965/1965%20-%200878.html |title=''A DC-8F has been bought by UTA, ....'', Air Transport ..., Flight International, 1 April 1965, p. 478 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2017-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006212514/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1965/1965%20-%200878.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

为顺利引进并运营麦道DC-10，法联航与[[荷兰皇家航空|荷兰皇家航空]]、[[北欧航空|北欧航空]]、瑞士航空合组KSSU<ref group=nb>联盟名称由四家航空公司的首字母依字母顺序组成</ref>维修联盟。<ref name="UTA_French_independent1"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1970/1970%20-%200415.html |title=''KSSU Signs up UTA'', Air Transport ..., Flight International, 12 March 1970, p. 371 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305200703/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1970/1970%20-%200415.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1972/1972%20-%203312.html |title=Air Transport, Flight International, 14 December 1972, p. 855 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306093817/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1972/1972%20-%203312.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1981年8月，法联航在瑞士航空之后成为[[波音747|波音747-300]]的第二个用户，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1983/1983%20-%200340.html |title=Air Transport, Flight International, 26 February 1983, p. 508 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2018-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314180122/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1983/1983%20-%200340.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>并于1983年3月2日接收第一架。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1983/1983%20-%200418.html |title=''747-300 deliveries begin'', World News, Flight International, 12 March 1983, p. 634 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2018-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315003830/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1983/1983%20-%200418.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>法联航也有两架[[波音747|波音747-200]]被改装为747-200SUD，<ref group=nb>'''SUD'''即“加长上层甲板（'''S'''tretched '''U'''pper '''D'''eck）”的简写</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%200296.html |title=''UTA stretches 747 top'', Air Transport, Flight International, 2 February 1985, p. 4 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2018-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315003824/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%200296.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="fleet_changes">{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%202345.html |title=''UTA streamlines fleet'', Air Transport, Flight International, 3 August 1985, p. 7 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2018-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315003758/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%202345.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>而其余对747-200进行如此改装的航空公司只有荷兰皇家航空（改装10架）及[[日本航空|日本航空]]（改装2架）。

1987年，法联航首次订购[[空中客车|空中客车]]客机，订单包括六架[[空中客车A340|空中客车A340-300]]，以及另外六架A340的选购权。<ref name="second_favourite2"/>这六架已订购的A340计划在1992年至1994年间交付使用<ref name="expansion"/><ref>[http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9B0DE2DB1E3BF93BA25755C0A961948260 The New York Times, 18 June 1987, COMPANY NEWS — Order for Airbus]</ref>，以替换老旧的DC-10。

1989年，法联航以海空包机公司的名义，斥资2.5亿美元订购了三架[[波音767|波音767-300ER]]。<ref name="second_favourite2"/><ref>[http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DEFDF1F3DF93AA25752C0A96F948260 The New York Times, 19 January 1989, BRIEFS]</ref>法航收购法联航之后也接收了海空公司的两架767-300ER。

