==意外事故==
[[File:Boeing_747-3B3,_UTA_-_Union_de_Transports_Aeriens_AN1453106.jpg|thumb]]
法国联合航空的飞机发生过5次有记录的事故，其中4次飞机报废，3次有人员死亡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/operator/airline.php?var=4692 |title=Union de Transports Aériens (UTA) at the Aviation Safety Network Database |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2006-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060928041622/http://www.aviation-safety.net/database/operator/airline.php?var=4692 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1964年10月2日，法联航的一架[[道格拉斯DC-6|道格拉斯DC-6B]]（编号为F-BHMS）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19641002-0&vnr=1&kind=PC |title=Douglas DC-6B F-BHMS (photo) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2006-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060216132226/http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19641002-0&vnr=1&kind=PC |dead-url=no }}</ref>在由马略卡岛帕尔马飞往[[努瓦迪布|努瓦迪布]]的途中撞上阿尔卡萨瓦山坠毁，机上80人（7名机组人员与73名乘客）全部遇难。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19641002-0 |title=Douglas DC-6B F-BHMS (accident report) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104080516/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19641002-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1972年7月12日，法联航一班由阿比让飞往巴黎的航班被劫持，2人死亡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19720712-1 |title=1972 hijack of Abidjan-Paris flight resulting in two deaths |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2007-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070922210103/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19720712-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1984年3月10日，法联航一架[[道格拉斯DC-8|道格拉斯DC-8-63PF]]（注册编号F-BOLL）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19840310-0&vnr=1&kind=PC |title=McDonnell Douglas DC-8-63PF F-BOLL (photo) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2006-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060214140935/http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19840310-0&vnr=1&kind=PC |dead-url=no }}</ref>由[[布拉柴维尔|布拉柴维尔]]经[[恩贾梅纳|恩贾梅纳]]飞往巴黎途中，在恩贾梅纳机场发生两次炸弹爆炸，飞机被炸毁，但因为机上所有人在放置于中部货舱的炸弹爆炸前逃生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19840310-0 |title=McDonnell Douglas DC-8-63PF F-BOLL (accident report) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2012-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012024837/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19840310-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="UTA_terrorism">{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1989/1989%20-%202952.html |title=''UTA DC-10 "mid-air explosion" investigated'', Operations: Safety, Flight International, 30 September 1989, p. 10 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2017-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818090047/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1989/1989%20-%202952.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1985年3月16日，法国联合航空一架[[波音747|波音747-3B3]]（注册编号F-GDUA）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19850316-1&vnr=1&kind=PC |title=Boeing 747-3B3 F-GDUA (photo) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2005-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050319082046/http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19850316-1&vnr=1&kind=PC |dead-url=no }}</ref>在巴黎戴高乐机场进行客舱清洁时全机烧毁，无人受伤或死亡。<ref name="fleet_changes"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19850316-1 |title=Boeing 747-3B3 F-GDUA (accident report) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2009-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090709094914/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19850316-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%201305.html |title=''Record 747 hull payment expected'', World News, Flight International, 4 May 1985, p. 3 |access-date=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305152336/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1985/1985%20-%201305.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1989年9月19日，[[法國聯合航空772號班機空難|法国联合航空772号班机]]，一架[[麦道DC-10|麦道DC-10]]（注册编号N54629）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19890919-1&vnr=1&kind=PC |title=McDonnell Douglas DC-10-30 N54629 (photo) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606083149/http://aviation-safety.net/photos/displayphoto.php?id=19890919-1&vnr=1&kind=PC |dead-url=no }}</ref>由布拉柴维尔经恩贾梅纳飞往巴黎，在从恩贾梅纳起飞后46分钟发生炸弹爆炸，机上156名乘客及14名机组人员全部遇难。<ref name="UTA_terrorism"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/3163621.stm |title=UTA 772: The forgotten flight |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2014-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140522090143/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/3163621.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19890919-1 |title=McDonnell Douglas DC-10-30 N54629 (accident report) |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2011-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111209181930/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19890919-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

